-	$15,000 TO THE BLACKSTONE RIVER WATERSHED COUNCIL/FRIENDS OF THE BLACKSTONE TO ENGAGE LOCAL COMMUNITIES VIA OUTREACH AND EDUCATION ACTIVITIES ON THE ECOLOGICAL AND SOCIAL VALUE OF A HEALTHY AND CONNECTED BLACKSTONE RIVER; AND
-	$909,800 FOR A REQUEST FOR PROPOSALS FOR ADDITIONAL PROJECT DEVELOPMENT (PRIORITIES TO BE DETERMINED) IN YEAR 2.
